<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>RentAHorse</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= stylesheet_pack_tag 'application' %>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload', defer: true %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%= render 'shared/navbar' %>
    <%= render 'shared/flashes' %>


    <%= yield %>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content container">

      <div class="footer-section about">
        <h1>Rent a Horse</h1>
        <p>
          Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorum ratione ducimus, repellendus quisquam vel at nemo odio delectus iure assumenda adipisci excepturi quibusdam obcaecati, reiciendis recusandae, totam iste expedita placeat?
